    ('alchemist-accelerator','Alchemist Accelerator','Enterprise startup accelerator built for technical teams selling to businesses and regulated markets.','https://www.alchemistaccelerator.com','Seed investment available',ARRAY['San Francisco','Remote'],ARRAY['Enterprise','Developer Tools','Fintech','Climate'], 'https://www.alchemistaccelerator.com','https://www.alchemistaccelerator.com','https://logo.clearbit.com/alchemistaccelerator.com',false,'6 months','Hybrid',ARRAY['seed'],ARRAY['Enterprise','Developer Tools','Fintech','Climate','Healthcare'],'Program equity terms apply','Seed capital, customer introductions, and enterprise mentor network',ARRAY['Global'],'Multiple cohorts; see accelerator page for current timing.','["LaunchDarkly","Rigetti","Mighty Buildings"]'::jsonb),
