    ('berkeley-skydeck','Berkeley SkyDeck','University-backed accelerator combining mentorship, office hours, and an optional investment vehicle.','https://skydeck.berkeley.edu','$200,000 fund option',ARRAY['Berkeley','Hybrid'],ARRAY['AI','Deep Tech','Climate','Healthtech'], 'https://skydeck.berkeley.edu','https://skydeck.berkeley.edu/apply/','https://logo.clearbit.com/skydeck.berkeley.edu',false,'6 months','Hybrid',ARRAY['pre-seed','seed'],ARRAY['AI','Deep Tech','Climate','Healthtech','Enterprise'],'Optional investment terms apply through SkyDeck Fund','Program support plus optional fund investment',ARRAY['Global'],'Seasonal batches; see application page for exact dates.','["Luma AI","Molekule","DeepScribe"]'::jsonb),
