    ('start-up-chile','Start-Up Chile','Public accelerator providing equity-free support, visas, and community for globally minded startups building from Chile.','https://startupchile.org','Equity-free grant support',ARRAY['Santiago'],ARRAY['SaaS','Fintech','Climate','Social Impact'], 'https://startupchile.org','https://startupchile.org','https://logo.clearbit.com/startupchile.org',false,'4 to 8 months','Hybrid',ARRAY['pre-seed','seed'],ARRAY['SaaS','Fintech','Climate','Social Impact','Consumer'],'No equity','Equity-free public support, coworking, and local ecosystem access',ARRAY['Global'],'Batch-based applications; see call page for current dates.','["The Not Company","Betterfly","Poliglota"]'::jsonb)
